01:38:19,860 --> 01:38:20,500
That...

2578
01:38:24,780 --> 01:38:28,800
It may be that real physics does

2579
01:38:28,800 --> 01:38:32,820
have an interchange symmetry between electric and magnetic,

2580
01:38:33,040 --> 01:38:35,520
electric charges becoming magnetic charges.

2581
01:38:35,920 --> 01:38:37,620
Now it's not really a symmetry

2582
01:38:37,620 --> 01:38:39,320
because if it was a symmetry,

2583
01:38:39,480 --> 01:38:41,740
we would have discovered those magnetic charges already.

2584
01:38:41,980 --> 01:38:44,700
They would have been similar to electrons.

2585
01:38:44,700 --> 01:38:47,130
They would have weighed the same thing as

2586
01:38:47,130 --> 01:38:49,560
electrons if there was a real symmetry between them.

2587
01:38:49,680 --> 01:38:52,100
And no such magnetic things exist.

2588
01:38:55,839 --> 01:38:59,140
So it is not a symmetry in the usual sense,

2589
01:38:59,140 --> 01:39:01,520
but we don't want to go there right now.

2590
01:39:01,580 --> 01:39:02,560
I'm too tired for it.

2591
01:39:03,000 --> 01:39:03,940
Any other questions?

2592
01:39:07,880 --> 01:39:08,400
Okay,

2593
01:39:08,400 --> 01:39:09,840
we've actually come a long way.

2594
01:39:09,900 --> 01:39:13,340
We've come through the Lagrangian formulation of mechanics,

2595
01:39:13,340 --> 01:39:15,700
the Lagrangian formulation of field theory,

2596
01:39:15,880 --> 01:39:18,040
the Lagrangian formulation of electrodynamics,

2597
01:39:18,120 --> 01:39:19,480
gauge invariance,

2598
01:39:19,480 --> 01:39:20,800
Lorentz invariance.

2599
01:39:20,900 --> 01:39:21,900
That's a lot of stuff.

2600
01:39:22,500 --> 01:39:23,640
That's a lot of stuff.

2601
01:39:24,020 --> 01:39:28,600
And as I said,

2602
01:39:28,600 --> 01:39:30,710
I think the only way to really digest

2603
01:39:30,710 --> 01:39:32,820
it is to go home with the equations

2604
01:39:32,820 --> 01:39:34,040
and work them out yourself,

2605
01:39:34,040 --> 01:39:37,700
starting from step one to step two.

2606
01:39:41,019 --> 01:39:42,120
So good luck.

2607
01:39:46,880 --> 01:39:47,940
For more,

2608
01:39:47,940 --> 01:39:50,340
please visit us at stanford.edu.

